name: DEEP IMPACT
description:
One of the iconographic moments and images that has been burned into the collective memory of mankind ever since is the moment when a lonely body falls down the building of a skyscraper in New York on 9/11. 
It is like the glistening fall of the Angel Lucifer down to Earth. 
.....a DEEP IMPACT
